Do not use Foundation or Bootstrap (or any layout framework).
Use HTML and Sass/Less/CSS.

You do not need to implement the nav (it does not have to actually drop down for mobile).

font-family: 'Muli', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
text-transform: lowercase;

------------------------------------------------


Layout 1
Max width of inner content is 1100px.

Layout 2
@1024px social media in nav disappears.

Layout 3
@900px "featured looks" disappears from nav
@900px product grid drops to 3 columns.

Layout 4
@768px layout switches to mobile
@768px product grid drops to 2 columns.

Layout 5 & 6
@635px product grid drops to 1 column.